From the North (Rice Lake/Superior)

	Follow US-53 South (51.8 miles). Take Exit 89 and turn left onto River Prairie Drive (0.3 mile). Turn left onto Rivers Edge Drive (0.2 mile). Orgel Wealth Management is located immediately to your left.
	(Google Map, Print Directions)

 
 
 
 
 
From the South (La Crosse)

	Take US-53 North until it becomes US-93 North (18.0 miles). Follow US-93 North and exit at US-53 North toward Superior (59.7 miles); take Exit 89 and turn right onto River Prairie Drive (1.9 miles), then left onto Rivers Edge Drive (0.3 mile). Orgel Wealth Management is located immediately to your left. 
	(Google Map, Print Directions)
 
 
 
 
 
From the Southeast (Madison/Milwaukee)

	Follow I-94 West toward Eau Claire. Take Exit 70 and veer right onto US-53 North (3.7 miles). Take Exit 89 and turn right onto River Prairie Drive (0.3 mile). Turn left onto Rivers Edge Drive (0.2 mile). Orgel Wealth Management is located immediately to your left. 2:50h
	(Google Map, Print Directions)

 
 
 
 
 
From the East (Wausau/Green Bay)

	Head West on WI-29 West/WI-29 Trunk West to US-53 South (88.7 miles). Take Exit 89 and turn left onto River Prairie Drive (0.3 mile). Turn left onto Rivers Edge Drive (0.2 mile). Orgel Wealth Management is located immediately to your left. 
	(Google Map, Print Directions)

 
 
 
 
 
From the East (Stevens Point)
Follow US-10 West toward Marshfield to the traffic circle (29.9 miles). Take the third exit, US-10 West. Merge right onto US-10 West, Klondike Drive (53.4 miles). Exit right onto I-94 West. Follow I-94 West toward Eau Claire (17.0 miles). Take Exit 70 and veer right onto US-53 North (3.7 miles). Take Exit 89 and turn right onto River Prairie Drive (0.3 mile). Turn left onto Rivers Edge Drive (0.2 mile). Orgel Wealth Management is located immediately to your left.
	(Google Map, Print Directions)

 
 
 
 
 
From the West (Minneapolis/St. Paul)
Follow I-94 East toward Eau Claire. Take Exit 70 and veer right onto US-53 North (3.7 miles). Take Exit 89 and turn right onto River Prairie Drive (0.3 mile). Turn left onto Rivers Edge Drive (0.2 mile). Orgel Wealth Management is located immediately to your left. 1:30h 
	(Google Map, Print Directions)

 
















